@startuml
[*] --> WaitingForSale : wait for a new sale
WaitingForSale --> AddingItems : item selected by customer
AddingItems --> AddingItems : item selected by customer
AddingItems --> PaymentReady : all items added
PaymentReady --> PaymentCash : pay with cash
PaymentReady --> PaymentVerification : verify payment (card or check)
PaymentVerification --> PaymentApproved : payment approved
PaymentCash --> SaleCompleted : complete sale immediately
PaymentApproved --> SaleCompleted : complete sale after verification
SaleCompleted --> WaitingForSale : return to waiting for next customer
@enduml
